                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="clear-both cf">
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Citadel Datathon</h4>
                        <img class="float-right ml-2 mb-2 w-28 lg:w-36" src="./index-images/datathon.jpg" />
                        <p>
